title: RuneScape (disambiguation)
content:
RuneScape may refer to:

  • Old School RuneScape, the game
    • Old School RuneScape Mobile, the mobile client
  • RuneScape, the live version of the original game
    • Earlier versions of RuneScape:
      • Devious MUD, the game that eventually became RuneScape Classic
      • RuneScape Classic
      • RuneScape 2, the historical version of RuneScape used as the base for Old School RuneScape.
  • Gielinor, the land the games take place in, often referred to as "RuneScape".
  • The official player-ran wikis
    • The Old School RuneScape Wiki
    • The RuneScape Wiki
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
